433
00:25:59,440 --> 00:26:00,790
Not a takeover.

434
00:26:02,160 --> 00:26:03,550
We fully recognize the contributions

435
00:26:03,720 --> 00:26:04,790
of the founding team.

436
00:26:05,270 --> 00:26:06,480
After we get rid of Hongwei Capital,

437
00:26:06,790 --> 00:26:08,240
I'll be there

438
00:26:08,640 --> 00:26:09,440
to help you

439
00:26:09,920 --> 00:26:11,590
make Miao Toys

440
00:26:11,590 --> 00:26:12,590
the best toy brand

441
00:26:12,640 --> 00:26:13,960
in China.

442
00:26:15,960 --> 00:26:16,720
I feel ashamed.

443
00:26:18,160 --> 00:26:19,240
That report

444
00:26:19,310 --> 00:26:20,680
pointed out

445
00:26:21,400 --> 00:26:22,200
some real problems.

446
00:26:23,240 --> 00:26:24,960
I've been reflecting.

447
00:26:25,880 --> 00:26:27,480
I didn't know enough,

448
00:26:28,400 --> 00:26:29,310
so I underestimated

449
00:26:29,350 --> 00:26:30,550
