450
00:26:30,920 --> 00:26:32,270
You're just burned out.

451
00:26:33,640 --> 00:26:35,110
You've been going nonstop for years.

452
00:26:35,400 --> 00:26:36,350
Never took a break.

453
00:26:37,160 --> 00:26:38,350
When you're extremely tired,

454
00:26:38,510 --> 00:26:40,160
it's easy to make mistakes.

455
00:26:40,590 --> 00:26:41,590
And this time,

456
00:26:41,640 --> 00:26:42,920
