464
00:26:57,200 --> 00:26:58,400
and get my team

465
00:26:58,790 --> 00:26:59,920
on board.

466
00:27:01,550 --> 00:27:02,270
No problem.

467
00:27:03,110 --> 00:27:03,750
By the way,

468
00:27:04,200 --> 00:27:05,030
are you really

469
00:27:05,240 --> 00:27:05,960
