473
00:27:12,550 --> 00:27:13,270
But honestly,

474
00:27:13,510 --> 00:27:14,510
there's another reason.

475
00:27:14,920 --> 00:27:16,200
There's some good news.

476
00:27:17,200 --> 00:27:17,790
Emily and I

477
00:27:18,070 --> 00:27:19,440
just had our third child.

478
00:27:21,640 --> 00:27:22,790
I genuinely feel

479
00:27:23,270 --> 00:27:24,240
if I could work in

480
00:27:24,960 --> 00:27:25,510
an industry

481
00:27:25,720 --> 00:27:27,270
that brings joy to kids,

482
00:27:27,830 --> 00:27:28,750
that would

483
00:27:28,960 --> 00:27:30,200
mean the world to me.

484
00:27:30,830 --> 00:27:31,590
Hence,

485
00:27:32,350 --> 00:27:33,000
I'm ready

486
00:27:33,110 --> 00:27:34,240
to give the rest of my career

487
00:27:34,640 --> 00:27:35,680
to this.

488
00:27:45,310 --> 00:27:45,920
Gao Xiang.

489
00:27:55,030 --> 00:27:55,640
All done?

490
00:27:57,000 --> 00:27:58,240
3.7%.

491
00:27:59,880 --> 00:28:00,590
Thanks.

492
00:28:03,510 --> 00:28:04,350
It was nothing.

493
00:28:09,720 --> 00:28:10,680
How many years

494
00:28:10,920 --> 00:28:12,790
