495
00:28:18,550 --> 00:28:19,790
You two must know.

496
00:28:20,750 --> 00:28:21,830
But you never told me.

497
00:28:23,270 --> 00:28:24,680
Doesn't matter how many years.

498
00:28:26,640 --> 00:28:27,830
We're still young.

499
00:28:30,640 --> 00:28:31,590
I like that.

500
00:28:36,200 --> 00:28:37,310
Don't you think

501
00:28:37,920 --> 00:28:39,110
this place

502
00:28:39,110 --> 00:28:40,550
