503
00:28:41,590 --> 00:28:43,160
A spaceship.

504
00:28:44,270 --> 00:28:45,750
I heard the design concept

505
00:28:46,310 --> 00:28:48,070
was to give the sky back to the people

506
00:28:48,880 --> 00:28:50,750
and make the skyscrapers
bow their heads.

507
00:28:51,590 --> 00:28:53,270
Never been here before.

508
00:28:54,640 --> 00:28:55,830
To me, this place

509
00:28:56,640 --> 00:28:57,790
takes a small space

510
00:28:58,000 --> 00:28:59,790
and makes it feel endless.

511
00:29:00,960 --> 00:29:02,480
Just like this city.

512
00:29:03,200 --> 00:29:04,270
Like a mirror

513
00:29:05,000 --> 00:29:06,310
showing the dreams and hopes

514
00:29:06,350 --> 00:29:07,480
