515
00:29:09,110 --> 00:29:10,310
Including the three of us.

516
00:29:31,160 --> 00:29:31,790
Wanzhi.

517
00:29:34,440 --> 00:29:35,510
I've waited

518
00:29:36,240 --> 00:29:37,400
