519
00:29:37,920 --> 00:29:39,590
I came all the way from
Hong Kong, China.

520
00:29:40,030 --> 00:29:41,310
I've asked you so many times.

521
00:29:42,240 --> 00:29:43,680
Why won't you see me?

522
00:29:44,200 --> 00:29:45,270
Is this really necessary?

523
00:29:46,400 --> 00:29:47,000
Wanzhi.

524
00:29:47,510 --> 00:29:48,720
Wanzhi, let me explain.

525
00:29:49,000 --> 00:29:49,920
What are you doing?

526
00:29:51,160 --> 00:29:51,790
Ms. Fang,

527
00:29:52,350 --> 00:29:53,790
