528
00:30:00,110 --> 00:30:00,880
Ms. Fang,

529
00:30:02,270 --> 00:30:03,550
anyway,

530
00:30:03,880 --> 00:30:05,000
Hongwei Capital

531
00:30:06,000 --> 00:30:07,160
is your company's

532
00:30:07,160 --> 00:30:07,960
No. 2 shareholder.

533
00:30:09,110 --> 00:30:10,680
I think we can sit and have a drink.

534
00:30:26,240 --> 00:30:27,030
Does it have to be

535
00:30:29,270 --> 00:30:30,440
this formal?

536
00:30:32,000 --> 00:30:33,200
Mr. Yan,

537
00:30:33,880 --> 00:30:34,510
I'm listening.

538
00:30:36,480 --> 00:30:37,550
I was hoping

539
00:30:37,790 --> 00:30:39,110
to take you to dinner.

540
00:30:39,640 --> 00:30:42,510
Even just barbecue.

541
00:30:43,070 --> 00:30:44,880
Then we could

542
00:30:45,110 --> 00:30:46,070
have some beer.

543
00:30:46,200 --> 00:30:47,030
Get to the point.

544
00:30:51,030 --> 00:30:51,920
After all,

545
00:30:53,110 --> 00:30:55,270
