546
00:30:56,480 --> 00:30:58,400
Do we really have to fight to the death?

547
00:31:00,440 --> 00:31:01,750
Who started this fight?

548
00:31:03,030 --> 00:31:03,960
Me?

549
00:31:05,310 --> 00:31:06,200
I admit it.

550
00:31:06,590 --> 00:31:07,310
It was me.

551
00:31:08,160 --> 00:31:10,000
But if not for you,

552
00:31:10,550 --> 00:31:11,640
how would I have

553
00:31:11,830 --> 00:31:12,720
invested that much?

554
00:31:12,920 --> 00:31:13,510
What?

555
00:31:13,960 --> 00:31:14,880
Want me to thank you?

556
00:31:16,790 --> 00:31:18,480
The reason I did all this

557
00:31:19,510 --> 00:31:21,030
was just to be with...

558
00:31:28,480 --> 00:31:29,160
Wanzhi,

559
00:31:29,590 --> 00:31:30,310
