560
00:31:30,880 --> 00:31:32,640
I finally got divorced last year.

561
00:31:34,110 --> 00:31:35,400
None of my business.

562
00:31:36,440 --> 00:31:37,510
Now I can

563
00:31:37,680 --> 00:31:39,350
