564
00:31:43,440 --> 00:31:43,960
Look.

565
00:31:44,030 --> 00:31:45,240
I brought a ring.

566
00:31:45,920 --> 00:31:47,680
My mom's really sick now.

567
00:31:47,960 --> 00:31:49,510
She already looked into you.

568
00:31:49,960 --> 00:31:51,400
She'd be all for it if you became

569
00:31:51,720 --> 00:31:52,590
her daughter-in-law.

570
00:31:52,830 --> 00:31:53,550
Then

571
00:31:53,790 --> 00:31:54,790
I could give you

572
00:31:54,880 --> 00:31:56,680
the entire toy division of Hongtu.

573
00:31:57,550 --> 00:31:59,070
You wouldn't lose anything.

574
00:31:59,270 --> 00:32:00,750
You would actually gain plenty.

575
00:32:01,160 --> 00:32:02,200
Including a share

576
00:32:02,720 --> 00:32:04,440
