586
00:32:26,160 --> 00:32:26,720
No.

587
00:32:27,240 --> 00:32:28,480
Your depravity

588
00:32:28,480 --> 00:32:29,790
is beyond belief.

589
00:32:31,830 --> 00:32:33,000
Money's good.

590
00:32:33,720 --> 00:32:35,720
But using it to do whatever you want

591
00:32:36,590 --> 00:32:38,110
just makes you a joke.

592
00:32:42,400 --> 00:32:44,400
You started this fight.

593
00:32:45,070 --> 00:32:46,200
And you're gonna

