633
00:35:15,360 --> 00:35:16,000
That's great.

634
00:35:16,230 --> 00:35:17,840
She's long overdue for a break, huh?

635
00:35:18,400 --> 00:35:19,000
Gao Xiang,

636
00:35:19,670 --> 00:35:20,590
what are you hiding

637
00:35:21,150 --> 00:35:22,590
about Yu County?

638
00:35:25,070 --> 00:35:25,880
Yu County?

639
00:35:26,960 --> 00:35:27,590
I...

