00:35:30,590 --> 00:35:32,110
I've made a few trips there.

641
00:35:33,320 --> 00:35:34,280
I kept quiet

642
00:35:34,510 --> 00:35:35,510
about Mr. Meng's illness

643
00:35:36,070 --> 00:35:37,150
because a promise

644
