I gave him my word.

646
00:35:40,800 --> 00:35:42,510
Please don't blame me.

647
00:35:44,710 --> 00:35:45,840
I remember you're

648
00:35:45,880 --> 00:35:47,150
Zhao Jun's angel investor.

649
00:35:48,760 --> 00:35:49,920
You're not going there?

650
00:35:57,440 --> 00:35:58,590
Can I take time off?

651
00:36:06,670 --> 00:36:09,030
Zhao Jun also invited Qian and me.

652
00:36:09,550 --> 00:36:10,280
We wanna

653
00:36:10,670 --> 00:36:12,360
visit Mr. Meng's grave.

654
00:36:16,550 --> 00:36:17,840
Will you go?

655
00:36:24,400 --> 00:36:25,440
I would be honored.

656
00:36:27,880 --> 00:36:29,320
(I used to think)

657
00:36:29,630 --> 00:36:32,920
(everyone's life was already written.)

658
00:36:34,230 --> 00:36:36,070
(Until I crossed mountains,)

659
00:36:36,670 --> 00:36:40,280
