and fall of the tide.)

662
00:36:47,070 --> 00:36:48,280
(Only then did I see:)

663
00:36:48,840 --> 00:36:49,710
(fate)

664
00:36:50,030 --> 00:36:53,760
(is the path)

665
00:36:53,960 --> 00:36:56,320
