668
00:37:07,920 --> 00:37:08,880
(One is from your parents.)

669
00:37:09,510 --> 00:37:10,550
(It decides)

670
00:37:10,550 --> 00:37:11,440
(your family)

671
00:37:11,800 --> 00:37:12,840
