683
00:37:26,360 --> 00:37:27,920
(The third comes from cultivation.)

684
00:37:28,670 --> 00:37:29,630
(Called Self-made Fate.)

685
00:37:31,510 --> 00:37:32,710
(Dating without purpose)

686
00:37:32,710 --> 00:37:33,480
(would hurt)

687
00:37:33,480 --> 00:37:34,710
