701
00:37:55,800 --> 00:37:57,360
(I've thought it through.)

702
00:37:58,360 --> 00:38:00,550
(I'll walk my own path.)

703
00:38:01,150 --> 00:38:02,110
(Wherever it leads,)

704
00:38:02,400 --> 00:38:03,480
(and whatever I become,)

705
00:38:04,320 --> 00:38:05,360
