706
00:38:05,760 --> 00:38:07,000
Sir, here's my resume.

707
00:38:07,400 --> 00:38:08,760
(I chose to come to Shenzhen)

708
00:38:09,510 --> 00:38:10,670
(and make my own way.)

709
00:38:11,070 --> 00:38:12,110
(My life and my fate)

710
00:38:13,320 --> 00:38:14,510
are mine to decide.

711
00:38:15,480 --> 00:38:16,480
(I came to Shenzhen)

712
00:38:16,510 --> 00:38:17,440
(because I wanted)

713
00:38:17,440 --> 00:38:18,670
