714
00:38:18,920 --> 00:38:19,840
(wanted to prove)

715
00:38:20,000 --> 00:38:21,760
(I could make it on my own.)

716
00:38:23,400 --> 00:38:24,480
(I want to try again.)

717
00:38:25,000 --> 00:38:25,880
(I can do it.)

718
00:38:26,230 --> 00:38:27,590
I don't want to give up.

719
00:38:31,840 --> 00:38:33,110
(I've realized)

720
00:38:33,840 --> 00:38:35,550
(if you let life beat you)

721
00:38:35,630 --> 00:38:36,510
(and just give up,)

722
00:38:37,070 --> 00:38:38,280
(it only gets more painful.)

723
00:38:39,480 --> 00:38:40,280
(Every time)

724
00:38:40,280 --> 00:38:41,840
(I think I can't go on,)

725
00:38:42,760 --> 00:38:44,000
(if I stick with it a bit more,)

726
00:38:44,590 --> 00:38:45,510
(I get through it.)

727
00:38:46,550 --> 00:38:47,550
(I don't want to give up.)

728
00:38:48,110 --> 00:38:49,480
(I want to fight one more time.)

729
00:39:10,000 --> 00:39:11,070
(To me,)

730
00:39:11,510 --> 00:39:12,800
(Yu County is a mountain.)

731
00:39:13,070 --> 00:39:14,670
(Quiet, solid, and heavy.)

732
00:39:14,920 --> 00:39:17,030
(It's my home, my starting point.)

733
00:39:17,630 --> 00:39:19,070
(Shenzhen is a sea.)

734
00:39:19,480 --> 00:39:20,760
(Endless and surging.)

735
00:39:21,320 --> 00:39:23,550
(It's my path, my dream.)

736
00:39:24,070 --> 00:39:25,590
(Mountain and sea)

737
00:39:25,800 --> 00:39:26,920
(together made me)

738
00:39:26,920 --> 00:39:29,150
(who I am.)

739
00:39:29,480 --> 00:39:30,400
(Ordinary,)

740
00:39:30,710 --> 00:39:32,880
(yet not quite.)

741
00:39:32,880 --> 00:39:33,960
(Fang Wanzhi!)

742
00:39:50,670 --> 00:39:52,000
(Fang Wanzhi!)

743
00:39:59,760 --> 00:40:00,670
(Wanzhi!)

744
00:40:01,510 --> 00:40:02,440
(Wanzhi!)

