766
00:42:05,000 --> 00:42:06,150
(Your eldest auntie.)

767
00:42:06,320 --> 00:42:07,920
(Your youngest auntie.)

768
00:42:09,320 --> 00:42:09,920
Auntie!

769
00:42:10,000 --> 00:42:10,840
Auntie!

770
00:42:14,710 --> 00:42:16,070
(Yang Hui, your cousin.)

771
00:42:16,150 --> 00:42:17,360
